Apply the 'vial' tool to these negative items, especially those combining a mundane solid and a magical solid (like rose petal + sunstone, or mushroom + sunstone), as this reliably yields 100 points. Be very cautious with the 'filter' tool; it generally reduced value or introduced 'botched filtering' for me.
